<%- include('../layout/head.ejs') %>
    <body>
        <%- include('../layout/header.ejs') %>
        <main>
            <section class="intro">
                OneSound aims to unite people of all cultures through the love of music. Users will select a genre of music or an artist they feel like listening to, and a playlist of songs from diverse cultures and languages will be generated. The world is vast, but we believe music is a universal language that can bring us all a little closer together.
            </section>

            <h2>How does it work?</h2>
            <section class="how-to-search">
                
                <figure>
                    <h3>Artist</h3>
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150">
                    <p>Search by artist to generate a playlist of similar artists from different countries around the world! Not sure where to start? Here are some examples below:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Meek Mill</li>
                        <li>Animal Collective</li>
                        <li>Bush</li>
                        <li>Ariana Grande</li>
                        <li>Odezsa</li>
                        <li>Backstreet Boys</li>
                    </ul>
                </figure>
                <figure>
                    <h3>Song Title</h3>
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150">
                    <p>Search by song title to generate a playlist of songs from around the world with the same title! Not sure where to start? Here are some examples of key words:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Reflections</li>
                        <li>Animals</li>
                        <li>Love</li>
                        <li>Boyfriend</li>
                        <li>Forever</li>
                        <li>Promise</li>
                    </ul>
                </figure>
                <figure>
                    <h3>Genre</h3>
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150">
                    <p>Search by genre to generate a playlist of songs from around the world with a similar genre! Not sure where to start? Here are some examples of key words:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Pop</li>
                        <li>Rock</li>
                        <li>EDM</li>
                        <li>Rap</li>
                        <li>Jazz</li>
                        <li>Traditional</li>
                    </ul>
                </figure>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../layout/footer.ejs') %>
    </body>
</html>